01:45:45.250 --> 01:45:55.670
What are you doing in my house?

01:45:55.670 --> 01:45:57.670
This isn't your house, Einstein.

01:45:57.670 --> 01:45:59.670
You're in cyberspace.

01:45:59.670 --> 01:46:00.670
Cyber what?

01:46:00.670 --> 01:46:02.670
Cyberspace.

01:46:02.670 --> 01:46:04.670
Virtual reality.

01:46:04.670 --> 01:46:07.670
You're still in the game, Einstein.

01:46:07.670 --> 01:46:10.670
Except that the rules have changed.

01:46:13.670 --> 01:46:16.670
What happened to the Knights of the Round Table?

01:46:16.670 --> 01:46:18.670
I bloom away.

01:46:18.670 --> 01:46:20.670
I'm a virus.

01:46:20.670 --> 01:46:22.670
That's what I do.

01:46:22.670 --> 01:46:24.670
A computer virus?

01:46:24.670 --> 01:46:26.670
How'd you get in here?

01:46:26.670 --> 01:46:28.670
All that matters now

01:46:28.670 --> 01:46:30.670
is how I'm getting out.

01:46:34.810 --> 01:46:37.810
Most viruses infect and destroy.

01:46:38.810 --> 01:46:41.810
But I'm smarter than that.

01:46:41.810 --> 01:46:44.810
I've got bigger plans.

01:46:47.810 --> 01:46:49.810
None of this is real, you know.

01:46:49.810 --> 01:46:53.810
It didn't go from the computer right into your head.

01:46:53.810 --> 01:46:57.810
But I've done a little reprogramming.

01:46:57.810 --> 01:46:59.810
I don't think you should mess with it.

01:46:59.810 --> 01:47:02.810
Too late. You've given me the perfect setup.

01:47:02.810 --> 01:47:04.810
What do you mean?

01:47:04.810 --> 01:47:07.810
Once my program runs,

01:47:07.810 --> 01:47:13.810
I'll be able to output myself from this stupid game.

01:47:13.810 --> 01:47:14.810
Right.

01:47:14.810 --> 01:47:16.810
Into your brain.

01:47:17.810 --> 01:47:18.810
What?

01:47:18.810 --> 01:47:20.810
When they turn off the game,

01:47:20.810 --> 01:47:23.810
I'm going to stay inside your brain.

01:47:23.810 --> 01:47:28.810
You're going to take me into the real world, Einstein.

01:47:29.810 --> 01:47:34.810
Where I can cause some real damage.

01:47:37.810 --> 01:47:39.810
I don't believe you.

01:47:39.810 --> 01:47:41.810
Oh, it's already started.

01:47:41.810 --> 01:47:43.810
Look at your hand.

01:47:47.350 --> 01:47:49.350
But this is a game. There has to be rules.

01:47:49.350 --> 01:47:51.350
Sure.

01:47:51.350 --> 01:47:53.350
Rule number one.

01:47:53.350 --> 01:47:55.350
I win.

01:47:55.350 --> 01:47:57.350
You lose.

01:47:57.350 --> 01:47:59.350
That's not fair.

01:47:59.350 --> 01:48:02.350
Okay, I'll be fair.

01:48:02.350 --> 01:48:05.350
You can escape from this game,

01:48:05.350 --> 01:48:07.350
but you've got only...

01:48:07.350 --> 01:48:12.350
Program will run in 10 minutes and 35 seconds.

01:48:12.350 --> 01:48:17.950
You heard it, Einstein. Good luck.

01:48:17.950 --> 01:48:32.320
So, what was it like to be one of the knights of the round table?

01:48:32.320 --> 01:48:34.320
There's something wrong. There's a virus in there.

01:48:34.320 --> 01:48:36.320
Virus? That's impossible.

01:48:36.320 --> 01:48:38.320
There is. Things are all wrong. You gotta...

01:48:38.320 --> 01:48:42.320
I will not sit still and let you insult my life's work.

01:48:42.320 --> 01:48:45.950
I said out!

01:48:45.950 --> 01:48:55.590
Hey, guys.

01:48:55.590 --> 01:49:02.080
What's the matter? You forgot your combo?

01:49:02.080 --> 01:49:03.080
Let's go, Evan.

01:49:03.080 --> 01:49:07.080
Sorry, going to the game with my girl.

01:49:07.080 --> 01:49:09.080
But, Evan! Evan!

01:49:09.080 --> 01:49:15.020
I'm still in the game.

01:49:15.020 --> 01:49:24.310
Open up.

01:49:24.310 --> 01:49:30.200
And Evan, open up.

01:49:30.200 --> 01:49:32.900
Voice.

01:49:32.900 --> 01:49:54.770
You're late.

01:49:54.770 --> 01:49:59.770
And this is the most important test of your life.

01:49:59.770 --> 01:50:02.770
Does anyone know what 2 plus 2 equals?

01:50:02.770 --> 01:50:03.770
5?

01:50:03.770 --> 01:50:05.770
Correct. Anyone else?

01:50:05.770 --> 01:50:09.790
10 minutes left.

01:50:09.790 --> 01:50:12.790
Correct. Simon.

01:50:12.790 --> 01:50:14.790
4.

01:50:14.790 --> 01:50:18.790
And exactly what formula did you use?

01:50:18.790 --> 01:50:35.320
We've got to get out of here.

01:50:35.320 --> 01:50:36.320
What did the virus say?

01:50:36.320 --> 01:50:41.680
We've got to reprogram the computer.

01:50:42.680 --> 01:50:47.680
Enjoying the game, Einstein?

01:50:47.680 --> 01:50:53.680
The speed of light divided by the speed of sound equals...

01:50:53.680 --> 01:50:54.680
5.

01:50:54.680 --> 01:50:57.680
5 minutes left.

01:50:57.680 --> 01:50:59.680
Relax.

01:50:59.680 --> 01:51:19.540
This is a horn. It may cause extreme warning.

01:51:19.540 --> 01:51:30.160
Hi, Simon. How's the game going?

01:51:30.160 --> 01:51:34.450
Evan?

01:51:34.450 --> 01:51:36.450
Is it really you?

01:51:36.450 --> 01:51:37.450
In the flesh.

01:51:37.450 --> 01:51:40.450
Evan, get me out of here. The thing's gone berserk.

01:51:40.450 --> 01:51:44.450
I know. Somebody planted a virus.

01:51:44.450 --> 01:51:47.450
It was you, wasn't it? Where's Poe?

01:51:47.450 --> 01:51:48.450
Still on the phone.

01:51:48.450 --> 01:51:51.450
But come on, Simon. I thought you could do anything.

01:51:51.450 --> 01:51:53.450
You can get out of this yourself.

01:51:53.450 --> 01:51:57.450
Two-minute warning. This is your two-minute warning.

01:51:57.450 --> 01:51:58.450
Did you see that?

01:51:58.450 --> 01:51:59.450
See what?

01:51:59.450 --> 01:52:02.960
The virus is coming for me, Evan.

01:52:02.960 --> 01:52:04.960
It's going to take away my brain.

01:52:04.960 --> 01:52:06.960
Get me out of here.

01:52:06.960 --> 01:52:09.960
Not until you apologize for all the things you did to me.

01:52:09.960 --> 01:52:10.960
What?

01:52:10.960 --> 01:52:12.960
It's your Evan's help.

01:52:12.960 --> 01:52:18.510
Not until you apologize...

01:52:18.510 --> 01:52:25.280
Anybody home?

01:52:25.280 --> 01:52:27.280
I'm sorry, alright?

01:52:27.280 --> 01:52:28.280
I don't believe you.

01:52:28.280 --> 01:52:30.280
I'm running out of time, Evan.

01:52:30.280 --> 01:52:33.280
Okay, relax. I programmed the virus myself.

01:52:33.280 --> 01:52:35.280
It won't do anything to you.

01:52:35.280 --> 01:52:37.280
No, what do you call this?

01:52:37.280 --> 01:52:39.280
Oh, no.

01:52:39.280 --> 01:52:42.280
Going up.

01:52:42.280 --> 01:52:46.280
Going up.

01:52:46.280 --> 01:52:50.270
That wasn't supposed to happen.

01:52:50.270 --> 01:52:52.270
He's running his own program. You've got to stop it.

01:52:52.270 --> 01:52:54.270
Okay. Okay, let me think.

01:52:54.270 --> 01:52:59.030
I just have to enter the abort code.

01:52:59.030 --> 01:53:01.030
It doesn't work. He's frozen me out.

01:53:01.030 --> 01:53:03.030
You know, unfreeze it.

01:53:03.030 --> 01:53:07.030
I can't. Nothing responds.

01:53:07.030 --> 01:53:10.030
Won't be long now.

01:53:10.030 --> 01:53:12.030
Evan!

01:53:12.030 --> 01:53:15.030
Okay. You can abort from in there, but you need the code.

01:53:15.030 --> 01:53:17.030
We'll give it to me.

01:53:17.030 --> 01:53:19.030
I bet you can figure out what it is.

01:53:19.030 --> 01:53:22.030
Just give it to me.

01:53:22.030 --> 01:53:25.030
Okay. The code is my copy.

01:53:25.030 --> 01:53:27.030
Evan?

01:53:27.030 --> 01:53:44.940
Evan? Calm, is it calm?

01:53:44.940 --> 01:53:45.940
Computer guy.

01:53:45.940 --> 01:54:01.550
Can't block me out, Einstein.

01:54:01.550 --> 01:54:06.720
If it's longer, come on.

01:54:06.720 --> 01:54:24.600
Guess you lose.

01:54:24.600 --> 01:54:39.890
Think so, Preston.

01:54:39.890 --> 01:54:44.890
