01:56:26.720 --> 01:56:29.720
What? No matter how bad a thing Evan did,

01:56:29.720 --> 01:56:31.720
the Simon always forgave him.

01:56:31.720 --> 01:56:33.720
You know what I liked about the story?

01:56:33.720 --> 01:56:34.720
